<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Macromedia downgraded.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Macromedia downgraded.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Bear Stearns cut its rating on Macromedia Inc to neutral from attractive, a Bear Stearns source said.</p>
<p>-- Late Thursday Macromedia reported a third quarter loss of $0.06 a share, far below analysts' expectations of a profit of $0.14.</p>
<p>-- Macromedia's shares dropped 3-4/4 to 9-3/4 in morning trading.</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street Desk 212-859-1730))</p>
